      <div class="w3-container">

<button onclick="myFunction('Demo1')" class="w3-btn w3-block w3-black w3-left-align"><b>How BAYADA can help you live safely at home</b></button>
<div id="Demo1" class="w3-container w3-hide">
  <section>
        <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 23px;">
          We understand that nothing is better than being in the comfort of home. But sometimes, it’s hard to manage everyday tasks on your own. Our trained and compassionate home health aides can help with activities such as:

    <ul style="list-style: disc; padding-left: 20px;">
      <li style="font-size: 24px;">Dressing, grooming, bathing, and using the toilet</li>
      <li style="font-size: 24px;">Meal planning and preparation</li>
      <li style="font-size: 24px;">Light housekeeping, laundry, and errands</li>
      <li style="font-size: 24px;">Medication reminders and picking up prescriptions</li>
      <li style="font-size: 24px;">Escort to doctor appointments</li>
      <li style="font-size: 24px;">Companionship</li>
    </ul>
        </p>
      </section>
</div><!-- Demo1 -->

