<div class="w3-container">

<button onclick="myFunction('Demo2')" class="w3-btn w3-block w3-black w3-left-align"><b>Why choose BAYADA?</b></button>
<div id="Demo2" class="w3-container w3-hide">
  <section>
        <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 23px;">
          Welcoming a home health caregiver into your home is a big decision—and a responsibility that we take very seriously. Here are just some of the many reasons to choose BAYADA for your or your loved one’s care:

    <ul style="list-style: disc; padding-left: 20px;">
      <li style="font-size: 24px;"><b>State Programs and Medicaid Waivers experts</b>—With more than 40 years of experience, we can help make it easy for you to get the services you need and are entitled to. </li>
      <li style="font-size: 24px;"><b>Largest provider of home health care in the Philadelphia region</b>—We serve more clients and employ more caregivers than any other local provider.</li>
      <li style="font-size: 24px;"><b>Caregivers you can trust</b>—Our hiring process includes criminal, reference, and background checks. All aides are trained, supervised, and fully-insured.</li>
      <li style="font-size: 24px;"><b>A care plan just for you</b>—We work with you to create a care plan to meet your specific needs.</li>
      <li style="font-size: 24px;"><b>Always available for you</b>—If you need assistance, you can reach a team member 24 hours a day, 7 days a week.</li>
      <li style="font-size: 24px;"><b>Free training for friend or family caregiver</b>—If you wish, you may have a friend or family member apply to be your BAYADA caregiver and we will provide training.</li>
      <li style="font-size: 24px;"><b>Highest standards of care</b>—We are accredited by Community Health Accreditation Partner (CHAP) for meeting the industry’s highest standards of care.</li>
